    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section id="about-us">

        <p>Thesis and Project Vault is an innovative web-based application designed to revolutionize how academic institutions manage and preserve final year project records. Traditionally, these records are stored in physical formats or scattered digital files, which are often difficult to access, prone to loss, and lack the collaborative potential that modern technology can offer.</p>
        <p>Our platform serves as a centralized digital repository where students, faculty, and alumni can securely store, access, and manage project documentation. By providing a structured and user-friendly interface, Thesis and Project Vault ensures the safekeeping of valuable academic work.</p>
    </section>

